# React/Next.js Standards

- Use functional components exclusively with proper React hooks
- Implement App Router patterns with proper route organization
- Follow React server component patterns - use server components by default
- Use client components only when needed for interactivity/hooks
- Implement proper data fetching strategies using React Server Components
- Use React suspense boundaries for loading states
- Properly implement error boundaries for error handling